15 certification from governmental units that deposits in the municipal
16 investment pool fund were first offered to a bank, savings and loan
17 association or savings bank in the preceding year; allowing eligible
18 financial institutions to file a complaint with the state treasurer upon the
19 failure of a governmental unit to comply with such certification;
20 establishing the investment rate for the pooled money investment board
